Don’t forget to have fun!

Lately, many companies stepped up their advertising game by becoming relatable to their audience. You can do the same! Have fun and put yourself in your audience’s shoes – how would you get your own attention?

There's only one success to be able to spend your life in your own way. Christopher Morley

I remember back in 2008 when I was a US Army recruiter and thinking about my exit plan from the US Army. I was listening to an audiobook by Timothy Ferriss the 4-Hour Work Week. It was right there that moment that I decided that I wanted to live a different way without having a boss. It was a scary moment for me and also the best moment for me. Here it is today 2017 thank the Lord I am still working from home. You can truly have your dreams come true if you believe them and have the faith. Using affirmations in having a positive mental attitude are just some of the drivers that will allow you to have the lifestyle you want to live. Read books study people who are successful and you shall have what you seek.  If you like this post please comment or like share with a friend who needs this today. "RAHSIA DI SEBALIK INSTAGRAM"
 yg bakal menggegarkan instagram anda tak lama lagi. 
_
""""""""""
APA YG KAMI AKAN KONGSIKAN?
""""""""""" _
Kami bakal bongkarkan rahsia bagaimana jerung instagram menjerung di instagram. Nak tau?
.
.
1- KENAPA INSTAGRAM
Rahsia kenapa jerung instagram memilih instagram sbgi tools marketing mereka sedangkan banyak lagi media sosial yg tak kurang hebatnya.
.
2- POWER PROFILE
Ini yang penting sebab prospek bukak jer instagram korg msti nmpk profile dlu, klu profile pon dh hampeh jgn harap dorg akan trus stalk ig korg!
.
3- HASHTAG
Parah dan sedih menyayat hati klu guna instagram tp xde hashtag. Pedih rasanya sebab Power of Hastag adalah di IG, tguk mcm mne jerung ig guna hashtag.
.
4- ENGAGEMENT 
Fuuuhhh ni part paling penting, kalau followers ratus ribu tp engagement rendah buat malu jer, bek duduk bawah katil. Engagement tulah sumber sales korg!!
.
5- 3 GOLONGAN
Dalam ig ni ada beberapa golongan, kne faham golongan ni baru senang nk pancing. Sebab tu jerung IG senyum jer pancing dalam instagram
.
6- BRANDING
Haaaaa, dalam ig pon boleh buat branding, x caya?? Tgk jenama besar2 semua ada ig sbb dorg buat branding lah. Tp kalau tak betul cara branding jd blander
.
7- KESELAMATAN
Bab penting sbb ramai yg dh x caya ngan instagram sbb bnyk kli hilang atau kene block. SALAH!! Sbb korg langgar rules. "TINGKATKAN FOLLOWERS, BRANDS DAN SALES"
.
.
